SUMMARY:Greek Smyrneika: An Immersive Concert Exploring Dance\, Music\, and
  Memory
DESCRIPTION:Join us for an immersive evening with Cafe Aman Project x KELEP
 OÚRI\, a collective of musicians and dancers rooted in the Smyrneiko trad
 ition — the music and dances of Asia Minor Greeks\, carried into the dia
 spora and transformed.Infused with a diasporic perspective\, the group bri
 ngs a fresh interpretation to the music and dances of Asia Minor Greeks wh
 ile honoring their cultural origins and embracing contemporary identity. I
 nspired by the historic Café Aman spaces of Asia Minor\, as well as moder
 n rebetika communities in Greece\, London\, and New York\, the collective 
 bridges histories\, cultures\, and identities through performance and coll
 aboration.Dance is central to each performance\, merging body and soul thr
 ough improvisational movement\, fluidity\, and feminine sensuality. Audien
 ces are invited into this shared experience through Tsifteteli and traditi
 onal line dances\, creating a space for connection and release.At its core
 \, the project reflects an evolving shift within NYC’s Greek subcultural
  spaces: an expansive and unapologetic expression of diasporic identity. T
 heir performances have become communal spaces where people across the dias
 pora can rediscover a sense of home\, belonging\, and cultural continuity.
 Evening Flow7:00 PM — Doors open. Settle in\, grab a drink\, and meet a 
 friend.7:30 PM — The evening begins: an opening set with song-by-song ex
 plorations of the Smyrneiko tradition\, the history of Asia Minor Greeks\,
  and the music that survived.8:30 PM — A short break with homemade snack
 s and Rose Saffron punch.9:00 PM — Encore: communal line dancing and Tsi
 fteteli.10:00 PM — Last call at the bar as we wind down the evening.This
  is a standing concert. If you need a seat\, reach out — we'll take care
  of you.What Is an Olio?Think Olio is an ongoing experiment in lifelong le
 arning. We are a community of open-minded people who gather to exchange id
 eas with new friends and connect over art\, literature\, and philosophy.Ch
 eck out our full calendarOur $30 membership gives you two events for the p
 rice of one!&nbsp\;An Olio is what we call the social learning events we
 ’ve been organizing since 2015. A blend between a lecture and a house pa
 rty\, Olios are led by a teacher who loves sharing their passions and the 
 room is filled with curious\, open-minded New Yorkers.&nbsp\;Our goal is t
 o spark new perspectives\, ignite curiosity\, and enjoy ourselves socially
 —an alternative to typical nightlife options.Disclaimer: By purchasing a
  ticket\, you agree to have your photo/video used for social media/marketi
 ng materials. If you prefer to not have your photo taken\, feel free to se
 nd us a note. Photo by Zhi-Da Zhong\n\nTickets & info: https://www.viewcy.
 com/event/smyrneika_exploring
URL:https://www.viewcy.com/event/smyrneika_exploring
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
