SUMMARY:An Olio House Party *Members Only
DESCRIPTION:Tickets:This is a member celebration!&nbsp\; To attend this par
 ty you can sign up for our monthly membership which gives you 2 free event
 s each month. &nbsp\;You will then be able to invite one friend to the par
 ty &lt\;3&nbsp\;What to expect:8pm: You're matched with new friends to dis
 cuss a couple of curated prompts.9:30pm-midnight: DJ Zimmy Dynamite begins
  and we dance our asses off until he winds down the evening with an ambien
 t set. We'll stretch and have tea because we love our bodies.What is Think
  Olio?Think Olio is an ongoing experiment in lifelong learning. We are a c
 ommunity of open-minded people who gather to exchange ideas with new frien
 ds and connect over art\, literature\, and philosophy.An Olio is what we c
 all the social learning events we’ve been organizing since 2015. A blend
  between a lecture and a house party\, Olios are led by a teacher who love
 s sharing their passions and the room is filled with curious\, open-minded
  New Yorkers.&nbsp\;Eight months into creating a venue\, one of our favori
 te feelings has been the moments where we’ve stepped outside of time. We
 ’ve created a space where conversations don’t feel rushed\, people are
  greeted with hugs\, and as a community\, we spontaneously come up with ne
 w ideas (like the dial-up-disco house party) and bring them to life.Our go
 al is to spark new perspectives\, ignite curiosity\, and enjoy ourselves s
 ocially—an alternative to typical nightlife options.Check out our full c
 alendarDisclaimer: By purchasing a ticket\, you agree to have your photo/v
 ideo used for social media/marketing materials. If you prefer to not have 
 your photo taken\, feel free to send us a note.\n\nTickets & info: https:/
 /www.viewcy.com/event/an_olio_house_party_
